===k&#333;an===
'''Noun'''

An apparently paradoxical [[anecdote]], used in [[Zen]] [[Buddhism]] to demonstrate the inadequacy of logical reasoning and to provoke [[enlightenment]].

Origin: Japanese, 'literally matter for public thought', from Chinese, gōngàn 'official business'.

